Building
=====
```
docker build -t carroarmato0/ffmpeg:v1 .
```

Launching the container
======
```
docker run -i -v ${PWD}:/root/workspace -t carroarmato0/ffmpeg:v1 /bin/bash
```

Compiling all the libraries and FFMPEG
======
```
cd ~
./build-all.sh;
```

Packaging FFMPEG
======
```
cd ~
./package-ffmpeg.rpm;
```
